title: Russell Westbrook and the Lakers at a Crossroads | Real Ones
description:
We’re halfway through the season and the Lakers are the gift that keeps on giving. Logan and Raja talk about the rumors that Frank Vogel’s job is in jeopardy, the Russell Westbrook experiment, and much more.
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
